HEADWORD: Collie
<hw>Col"lie</hw> <pr>(k⟦ocr⟧l"l⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gael.
<ets>cuilean</ets> whelp, puppy, dog.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The
Scotch shepherd dog. There are two breeds, the rough-haired and
smooth-haired. It is remarkable for its intelligence, displayed
especially in caring for flocks.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>colly</asp>, <asp>colley</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
